== PopraviMK

  * Mobile application for http://popravi.mk - public service for reporting urban problems.
  * Winner of the Android Vip contest: http://android.vip.mk/winners

== Development

  * Change host for devepeloment environment
    Change development_host variable in Resources/js/helpers/config.js file

  * When building does not work, touch tiapp.xml file to forse re-build

== Production

  * Add production google maps api key to tiapp.xml file
    <property name="ti.android.google.map.api.key.production">YOURKEY</property>

